# Sovereign ID: 1
# Copyright (c) 2024-2025 Jonathan Sherman. All Rights Reserved.
# Signature: Sm9uYXRoYW4gU2hlcm1hbjo6U292ZXJlaWduOjoxOjpPcmFjbGVBSTo6USsrUlM=
